pve-microvm (0.1.1-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Fix: include vmlinuz kernel in .deb (clean target was deleting it).
  * Fix: regex patch now produces valid Machine.pm (rewrote patcher in Python).
  * Tested on live PVE 9.1.7 node (z83ii): qm create/destroy works.

 -- Rui Carmo <rui.carmo@gmail.com>  Fri, 18 Apr 2026 15:30:00 +0000

pve-microvm (0.1.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release targeting Proxmox VE 9.0 (Debian Trixie).
  * Tested against qemu-server 9.1.6, pve-qemu-kvm 10.2.1 (QEMU 10.2).
  * Patch qemu-server Machine.pm to allow microvm machine type.
  * Add PVE::QemuServer::MicroVM module for microvm command generation.
  * Ship pve-oci-import helper for OCI-to-microvm disk conversion.
  * Include Firecracker-based kernel config with PVE overlay.

 -- Rui Carmo <rui.carmo@gmail.com>  Fri, 18 Apr 2026 13:00:00 +0000
